text: Sucker Punch is a 2011 fantasy and action movie. It is about a young woman put in a mental institution. She plans to escape the hospital. Emily Browning plays Babydoll. Jena Malone plays Rocket. Abbie Cornish plays Sweet Pea. This movie was released on March 25, 2011. It had a PG-13 rating. Category:2010s action movies Category:2011 movies
title: Sucker Punch (movie)
